        {
            "id": "DJN_SN20250824001269:0",
            "title": "Keurig Dr Pepper reportedly near $18 billion deal to buy coffee company JDE Peet's",
            "description": "<div class=\"body-KX2tCBZq body-pIO_GYwT content-pIO_GYwT\"><div class=\"symbolsContainer-cBh_FN2P logosContainer-cwMMKgmm\" data-no-swipe=\"true\"></div><div><span><p class=\"\"><span>By Mike Murphy</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>A pedestrian walks by a Peet's Coffee store in San Francisco in 2024</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Keurig Dr Pepper Inc. is closing in on a roughly $18 billion deal to acquire the Dutch coffee company JDE Peet's NV, the Wall Street Journal reported late Sunday.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>If the deal goes through, the combined company would split its beverage and coffee units, the Journal reported, effectively unwinding the 2018 deal that merged Dr Pepper and Keurig. Analysts questioned the wisdom of that deal at the time, and while the company's beverage unit has thrived, its coffee segment has struggled.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Neither company immediately responded to requests for comment late Sunday.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Texas-based Keurig Dr Pepper has a market cap of nearly $48 billion, and owns a portfolio of more than 125 brands, including 7-Up, Canada Dry, Snapple, Tully's Coffee and Green Mountain coffee.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>Amsterdam-based JDE Peet's has a market cap of around $15 billion, with brands that include Peet's Coffee, Stumptown Coffee Roasters and Maxwell House.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>JDE Peet's (NL:JDEP) Dutch-traded shares have surged about 61% year to date. Keurig Dr Pepper stock (KDP) is up about 9% in 2025, compared to the S&amp;P 500's SPX 10% gain.</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>-Mike Murphy</span></p><p class=\"\"><span>This content was created by MarketWatch, which is operated by Dow Jones &amp; Co. MarketWatch is published independently from Dow Jones Newswires and The Wall Street Journal.</span></p></span></div></div>",
            "link": "https://www.tradingview.com/news/DJN_SN20250824001269:0/",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-25 07:21:00",
            "source": "MarketWatch",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "en"
        },
